==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: xiŭ mù bù kĕ diāo
===Etymology===
*From the ''[[w:Analects of Confucius|Analects of Confucius]]''
**Literally: One cannot make a carving from rotten wood.
===Proverb===
'''[[朽]][[木]][[不]][[可]][[雕]]'''
#   You can't get pete from a tree; You can't teach a student that doesn't have the aptitude.
